  <entry>
    <title>Twikoo 表情包修改</title>
    <link href="https://blog.xiowo.net/posts/759e8c74.html"/>
    <id>https://blog.xiowo.net/posts/759e8c74.html</id>
    <published>2023-07-31T09:17:22.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-07-31T02:44:45.520Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近刚把博客搭好，看别人的 Twikoo 都自定义表情包，于是我也研究了一下</p><h2 id="可能用到的"><a href="#可能用到的" class="headerlink" title="可能用到的"></a>可能用到的</h2><p>大佬整理的表情包可以从 GitHub项目<a href="https://github.com/2X-ercha/Twikoo-Magic">Twikoo-Magic</a>或<a href="https://emotion.xiaokang.me/">小康的表情速查</a> 中找到</p><h2 id="修改"><a href="#修改" class="headerlink" title="修改"></a>修改</h2><p>Twikoo 的表情使用的是 <code>OwO</code> ,所以表情配置为一个 json 文件</p><blockquote><p>json 文件对格式要求严格，例如键与值都需要使用双引号进行包裹，如果是最后一项那么结尾不能包含逗号，可见<a href="https://www.runoob.com/json/json-tutorial.html"> 菜鸟教程</a></p></blockquote><p>不过我们目前不需要了解那么深入</p><p>在表情速查里复制Twikoo适配的 json 代码，以 <code>阿鲁</code> 为例：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;aru&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;image&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;container&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;aru-1&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;icon&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://7.dusays.com/2021/01/15/3c76dffbc08a5.png&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">..........</span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;aru-99&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;icon&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://7.dusays.com/2021/01/15/a5cf180e2f22a.png&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制多个记得做修改，删除上一个表情末尾的一个<code>&#125;</code> 然后添加 <code>,</code>  再把第二个开头的 <code>&#123;</code> 删除 ，以 <code>阿鲁</code> 和 <code>blob</code> 为例：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;aru&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;image&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;container&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;aru-1&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;icon&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://7.dusays.com/2021/01/15/3c76dffbc08a5.png&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;aru-99&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;icon&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://7.dusays.com/2021/01/15/a5cf180e2f22a.png&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;blob&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;image&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;container&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;blob-RedTick&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;icon&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://7.dusays.com/2021/01/15/c8407d638ca85.png&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;blob-wumpusblob&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;icon&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;img src=&#x27;https://7.dusays.com/2021/01/15/309dc42e77869.png&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以前往 <a href="https://www.bejson.com/">在线JSON格式化验证工具</a> 检查是否有误</p><p>最后将 json 文件上传服务器即可</p><h3 id="Twikoo-配置"><a href="#Twikoo-配置" class="headerlink" title="Twikoo 配置"></a>Twikoo 配置</h3><p>进入你的 Twikoo 控制台<br>找到 <code>插件</code> &gt; <code>EMOTION_CDN</code>  填入 <code>你的Json链接</code></p><p><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2023/07/31/64c7837761d76.png" alt="Twikoo 配置"></p><p>上面那个 <code>SHOW_EMOTION</code> 可以不用设置因为它默认就是 true </p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;最近刚把博客搭好，看别人的 Twikoo 都自定义表情包，于是我也研究了一下&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;可能用到的&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#可能用到的&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;可能用到的&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;可能用到的&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;大佬整理的表情包可以从 </summary>
      
    
    
    
