  <entry>
    <title>SEO优化：Hexo-abbrlink插件生成永久固定链接</title>
    <link href="https://blog.xiowo.net/posts/a1e8a28a.html"/>
    <id>https://blog.xiowo.net/posts/a1e8a28a.html</id>
    <published>2023-07-23T01:54:17.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-07-23T11:02:15.048Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前提"><a href="#前提" class="headerlink" title="前提"></a>前提</h2><p>首先Hexo默认的静态URL格式是 :year&#x2F;:month&#x2F;:day&#x2F;:title，即年、月、日、标题来生成固定链接的。如hexo生成的第一篇默认的文章为<a href="http://xiowo.net/2023/07/23/hello-world%E3%80%82">http://xiowo.net/2023/07/23/hello-world。</a></p><p>这种默认配置的缺点就是一般文件名是中文，导致url链接里有中文出现，分享出去的话中文就会转为UTF-8编码，导致文章链接又臭又长，不利于seo。</p><p>使用 hexo-abbrlink 插件可以完美解决，具体使用方法如下：</p><h2 id="安装插件"><a href="#安装插件" class="headerlink" title="安装插件"></a>安装插件</h2><p>对于abbrlik插件可详见项目源地址：<a href="https://github.com/rozbo/hexo-abbrlink">Github</a></p><p>视频教程可见安知鱼大佬的b站视频</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=644553654&bvid=BV1oY4y1c7p2&cid=804499261&page=1&autoplay=0" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true" autoplay=0> </iframe><h4 id="安装依赖"><a href="#安装依赖" class="headerlink" title="安装依赖"></a>安装依赖</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改 hexo  <code>config.yml</code> 文件中的永久链接为</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">posts/:abbrlink.html</span> <span class="comment"># 此处可以自己设置，也可以直接使用 :/abbrlink</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将以下内容复制到 hexo  <code>config.yml </code> 的最底下</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># abbrlink config</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">abbrlink:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">alg:</span> <span class="string">crc32</span>      <span class="comment">#support crc16(default) and crc32</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">rep:</span> <span class="string">hex</span>        <span class="comment">#support dec(default) and hex</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="生成链接示例"><a href="#生成链接示例" class="headerlink" title="生成链接示例"></a>生成链接示例</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">crc16 &amp; hex</span><br><span class="line">https://xiowo.net/posts/55c6.html</span><br><span class="line">crc16 &amp; dec</span><br><span class="line">https://xiowo.net/posts/43212.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">crc32 &amp; hex</span><br><span class="line">https://xiowo.bet/posts/6ec16a2c.html</span><br><span class="line">crc32 &amp; dec</span><br><span class="line">https://xiowo.net/posts/1521457752.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="注意"><a href="#注意" class="headerlink" title="注意"></a>注意</h2><p>对于先前已有文章的，请使用 <code>hexo clean</code> 清除以前生成的文章缓存，然后 <code>hexo g</code> 重新渲染即可</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
